          <li><strong>Built for tattoo:</strong> Generic booking tools lack consent forms, deposits, and industry-specific features.</li>
          <li><strong>Mobile-friendly:</strong> You and your clients live on phones. The software should too.</li>
          <li><strong>Deposit collection:</strong> If it doesn't collect deposits at booking, no-shows will kill you.</li>
          <li><strong>Simple pricing:</strong> Avoid per-booking fees that punish success.</li>
          <li><strong>Free trial:</strong> Test with real clients before committing.</li>
        </ul>

