        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>No deposit collection at booking</li>
          <li>Per-booking or per-client fees</li>
          <li>No digital consent forms</li>
          <li>Can't store reference images</li>
          <li>No SMS reminders (or they cost extra)</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Related: <a href="/blog/best-tattoo-studio-software/" class="text-brand-red hover:underline">Best Tattoo Studio Software Comparison</a></p>

